content.rendered:
Directed by Anil Ravipudi

Written by Anil Ravipudi. Anil Ravipudi. Anil Ravipudi. G. Adi Narayana. Narra Praveen

Cast Tamannaah Bhatia (Harika). Prakash Raj (Dora Swamy Naidu). Venkatesh Daggubati (Venky). Varun Tej (Varun). Nassar (Viswanath (Indian Embassy)). Rajendra Prasad (Prasad (as Rajendraprasad)). Anasuya Bharadwaj (Anasuya). Vennela Kishore (John Strow). Rajshri Nair (Dora Swamy Naidu’s wife). Mehreen Pirzada (Honey). Brahmaji (Albert Narayan Das). Easwari Rao (Viswanath’s wife). Satyam Rajesh (Dora Swamy Naidu’s Younger Son).Rajitha. Pragathi (Harika & Honey’s mother). Raghu Babu (MLA Anji Reddy). Priyadarshi Pulikonda (Darshi (as Priyadarshi)). Subbaraju (Dora Swamy Naidu Elder’s Son). Prudhviraj (Dora Swamy Naidu’s Elder Brother). Jhansi (Kanthamma). Joy Badlani. Srinivasa Reddy (ora Swamy Naidu Servant). Annapoorna (Harika & Honey’s grandmothe). Hari Teja (Dora Swamy Naidu’s sister). Duvvasi Mohan. Rocket Raghava (Salesman). Jaroslav Shvets (Czech policeman). Racha Ravi. Mirchi Kiran (MLA’s bodyguard). Vijaya Y..Jabardasth Rajamouli. Nutan Naidu (Nutan). Gemini Suresh. Chammak Chandra. Alka Rathod (Anasuya’s sister). Sunitha Manohar. Viva Raghav. Sivannarayana (Principal). Prabhavathi. Chakravarthii. Pradeep (Harika & Honey’s father). L. Vijaya (Harika & Honey’s grandmother). Siri. Padmavathi. Chintu. Muni Raju. Sathyasai Srinivas

Languages Telugu

Producers Sahni Bob. Ivano Fucci. Bandi Ratna Kumar. Lakshman. Dil Raju. Harshith Reddy. Sireesh

Production Sri Venkateswara Creation
